Uses of Package
org.sbml.squeezer

  • Packages that use org.sbml.squeezer 
    Package Description
    org.sbml.squeezer
    This is the core of SBMLsqueezer as it contains the central classes for reaction type analysis, kineticl law generation and some specialized exceptions.
    org.sbml.squeezer.celldesigner
    This package contains all necessary classes for the interaction between CellDesigner and SBMLsqueezer.
    org.sbml.squeezer.gui
    This package contains all necessary classes for the graphical user interface.
    org.sbml.squeezer.gui.wizard
    This package contains classes of the graphical user interface for the wizard that helps users to generate kinetic equations in one single step for the entire model.
    org.sbml.squeezer.kinetics
    This package contains one class for each supported kinetic law.
    org.sbml.squeezer.sabiork.wizard
    This package contains the basic user interface wizard for the search in SABIO-RK.
    org.sbml.squeezer.sabiork.wizard.gui
    The classes in this package are required for the graphical user interface of the SABIO-RK wizard.
    org.sbml.squeezer.sabiork.wizard.model
    The model behind the SABIO-RK wizard can be found in this package.
    org.sbml.squeezer.util
    General utility functions are maintained in this package.
  • Classes in org.sbml.squeezer used by org.sbml.squeezer 
    Class and Description
    RateLawNotApplicableException
    An exception to be thrown if the selected kinetics is not applicable to the given reaction.
    ReactionType
    The purpose of this class is to analyze a reaction object for several properties, such as the number of reactants and products, the types of modifiers and their number, if the stoichiometries are always integer numbers or real valued and much more.
    UnitConsistencyType
    This is an enumeration of the two possible ways of how to ensure consistent units within an SBML model; reacting species might either be given in molecule counts (UnitConsistencyType.amount) or their UnitConsistencyType.concentration.
    UnitFactory
    A factory class that creates frequently used instances of Unit and UnitDefinition if these are not yet present in a Model.
  • Classes in org.sbml.squeezer used by org.sbml.squeezer.celldesigner 
    Class and Description
    SBMLsqueezer
    The main program of SBMLsqueezer.
  • Classes in org.sbml.squeezer used by org.sbml.squeezer.gui 
    Class and Description
